
= render 'templates/search-header', categories: @categories

.main

  .main__visual
    = image_tag "main/visual/bg-mainVisual-pict_pc.jpg", class:"main__visual__image"
    .main__visual__content
      .main__visual__content__title
        人生を変えるフリマアプリ
      %p.main__visual__content__subtitle
        FURIMAはだれでもかんたんに出品・購入できる
        %br
        フリマアプリです
      .main__visual__content__icons
        = image_tag "main/visual/apple_logo.svg", size:"180x60", class:"main__visual__content__icons__apple"
        = image_tag "main/visual/google-play-badge.png", size:"230x90", class:"main__visual__content__icons__goo"

        
  .main__service
    .main__service__text
      FURIMAが選ばれる3つの理由 
      .main__service__text__underline
        .main__service__text__underline__content

    %ul.main__service__features
      %li.main__service__features__reason
        .main__service__features__reason__image
          .main__service__features__reason__image__number 1
          = image_tag "main/service/reason-01.jpg", size:"300x300", class:".main__service__features__reason__image__tag"
        .main__service__features__reason__title
          %span３分
          ですぐに出品
        .main__service__features__reason__subtitle 
          スマホで入力するだけで簡単に出品できる！

      %li.main__service__features__reason
        .main__service__features__reason__image
          .main__service__features__reason__image__number 2
          = image_tag "main/service/reason-02.jpg", size:"300x300", class:".main__service__features__reason__image__tag"
        .main__service__features__reason__title
          %spanシンプル
          で使いやすい
        .main__service__features__reason__subtitle
          めんどくさい入力は必要なく、検索も購入もスムーズ！ 

      %li.main__service__features__reason
        .main__service__features__reason__image 
          .main__service__features__reason__image__number 3    
          = image_tag "main/service/reason-03.jpg", size:"300x300", class:".main__service__features__reason__image__tag"
        .main__service__features__reason__title
          手数料
          %span業界最安
        .main__service__features__reason__subtitle
          最大3%でお得に出品&購入！


  .main__topshare
    = image_tag "main/topshare/phone-pic.jpg", class:"main__topshare__image"
    .main__topshare__content
      .main__topshare__content__title
        会員数日本一位
      %p.main__topshare__content__subtitle
        FURIMAは、フリマアプリで最も人気。
        %br
        出品・購入回数も業界最多です！
        %br
        ほしかったあの商品に出会えるかもしれません。
      .main__topshare__content__icons
        = image_tag "main/visual/apple_logo.svg", size:"180x60", class:"main__topshare__content__icons__apple"
        = image_tag "main/visual/google-play-badge.png", size:"230x90", class:"main__topshare__content__icons__goo"


  .main__function
    .main__function__text
      FURIMAの特徴
      .main__function__text__underline
        .main__function__text__underline__content

    %ul.main__function__features
      %li.main__function__features__reason
        .main__function__features__reason__image
          = image_tag "main/service/icon-01.png", size:"220x330", class:".main__function__features__reason__image__tag"
        .main__function__features__reason__title
          簡単に売り買いできる
        .main__function__features__reason__subtitle 
          スマホひとつで、いつでもどこでも簡単に出品・購入が可能！

      %li.main__function__features__reason
        .main__function__features__reason__image
          = image_tag "main/service/icon-03.png", size:"220x330", class:".main__function__features__reason__image__tag"
        .main__function__features__reason__title
          売上金は即日振込みに対応
        .main__function__features__reason__subtitle
          午前9時までに振込を依頼いただければ、翌日に指定の口座に入金いたします!

      %li.main__function__features__reason
        .main__function__features__reason__image 
          = image_tag "main/service/icon-04.png", size:"220x330", class:".main__service__features__reason__image__tag"
        .main__function__features__reason__title
          様々な支払いに対応
        .main__function__features__reason__subtitle
          お支払いは、クレジットカードだけでなく、ポイントや売上金など多彩な方法があります。


  .main__pickup
    .main__pickup__categories
      .main__pickup__categories__title
        ピックアップカテゴリー
      .main__pickup__categories__new-items
        = link_to "新規登録商品", '#', class:'main__pickup__categories__new-items--link'
      .main__pickup__categories__products
        - @products.each_with_index do |product, n|
          .main__pickup__categories__products__item
            = render 'templates/product-overview', product: product
          
    .main__pickup__brand
      .main__pickup__brand__title
        ピックアップブランド
      .main__pickup__brand__new-items
        = link_to "アーカイバ", '#', class:'main__pickup__brand__new-items--link'
      %ul.main__pickup__brand__products
        - @products.each_with_index do |product, n|
          .main__pickup__brand__products__item
            = render 'templates/product-overview', product: product

= render 'templates/download-footer'